# Chat Rules

## Purpose
Realtime chat per PRD 4.7 and BR-CH* in BUSINESS_RULES.

## Requirements
- Socket.io namespace per tenant; JWT auth on handshake.
- Conversations link tenant_id, optional inquiry_id, property_id.
- Auto-assign unassigned after 5 min round-robin BR-CH01.
- Manager sees all; executive assigned only BR-CH04.
- Sanitize message HTML (DOMPurify) before store/display.
- Emit `chat.message` to room participants.

## Restrictions
- No cross-tenant socket rooms.
- Client cannot access other users' conversations.

## Best Practices
- Redis adapter for horizontal scale.
- Link new website chat to inquiry if phone/email captured.
- Typing indicators optional Phase 6 stretch.

## Anti-Patterns
- Storing messages without tenant_id.
- Polling-only chat without websockets for agent inbox.

## Examples

```typescript
@SubscribeMessage('message')
async handleMessage(@ConnectedSocket() client, @MessageBody() dto: SendMessageDto) {
  await this.chatService.assertAccess(client.user, dto.conversationId);
  return this.chatService.sendMessage(dto, client.user);
}
```
